data.description: Your DREAM HOME!  This beautiful home sits on the corner of a 1.57-acre cul-da-sac lot with amazing views, a sparkling pool, & lots of room for entertainment. Great room features high, vaulted ceilings, stacked stone, & gas fireplace. Kitchen has 2 sinks, pantry, planning desk, eat-in area, & breakfast room. The owner's suite on main level boasts a glamour bath & private office/sitting room. Glamour bath incl. large walk-in closet, whirlpool tub, plus a shower. Partially finished basement space is perfect for rec room, family room, bar, guest sleeping area, workshop, workout room, & more. Oversized 2-Car garage on main level plus another garage in workshop area.  Chicken coop & outbldg incl.
